      <div>
        <h3><strong>Solving The UX Problem</strong></h3>
        <p>It was important to create a simple and natural conversation model, so users only need to supply an artist&#x27;s name.<br><br>We also relied on some training behaviors online and in-vehicle to familiarize users with the &quot;Radio&quot; suffix, following an artist&#x27;s name within SiriusXM.<br></p>
      </div>
