      <div>
        <h3><strong>Taking Inventory</strong></h3>
        <p>I started by mapping out the basic interactions of the Pandora Skill, which included the ability to:<br></p>
        <ul role="list" class="list-3">
          <li class="paragraph">Create a Pandora Station</li>
          <li class="paragraph">Like or Dislike a song</li>
          <li class="paragraph">Skip to the next song in the queue</li>
          <li class="paragraph">Favorite a Pandora station</li>
          <li class="paragraph">Learn the Song or Artist name</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
